FBIS4-36669 "drnes113_j_94038" FBIS-NES-94-113 Daily Report 12 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Aden Denies Shelling of al-Mukalla Airport Aden Denies Shelling of al-Mukalla Airport EA1206172594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 12 Jun 94 EA1206172594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 12 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Excerpt] A responsible source at the Defense Ministry of the Democratic Republic of Yemen has categorically denied that Rayyan Airport [serving al-Mukalla] had been rendered inoperable or had suffered any kind of damage. The source said all democratic Yemen's airports with the exception of that at Ataq were operational. The source expressed amazement that it was Israel radio which had carried the report by the military spokesman in Sanaa that northern forces yesterday evening allegedly shelled al-Mukalla's airport. [passage omitted]
